Package: neurobase
Type: Package
Title: 'Neuroconductor' Base Package with Helper Functions for 'nifti'
        Objects
Version: 1.27.11
Authors@R: person(given = "John", family = "Muschelli", role = c("aut",
        "cre"), email = "muschellij2@gmail.com")
Maintainer: John Muschelli <muschellij2@gmail.com>
Description: Base package for 'Neuroconductor', which includes many
        helper functions that interact with objects of class 'nifti',
        implemented by package 'oro.nifti', for reading/writing and
        also other manipulation functions.
Imports: methods, abind, matrixStats, R.utils, graphics, grDevices,
        stats, RNifti
